snippet.title: Pucca Jam Flash Game (All Pucca & Garu Levels)
snippet.description:
Just a Heads Up!:

If this video gets COPPA-fied, I am deleting it because I don't want children following me. Night Ol Master is not a kids channel, it's more for 13+ and Up. I mostly do PG videos but sometimes it goes for 13+ to mature audiences.
_____________________________________________________________
Here is the full gameplay of me playing one of personal favorite Pucca flash games called Pucca Jam.I love this game since watched the show when it used to be on Netflix of 2011-2014.

The Pucca Jam music have to be a sped up version of Buddha's Kontekst due to copyright from the Pucca Theme Song.

The original cut of this video:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hgItFa_o6g8WIiI2uaX6xQgvzNHvw2fB/view?usp=sharing

UPDATE 2-18-21: Since Flash got blocked in January 12th, you can’t play it anymore... :\
